title: 109:  Best 5 Defensive Players & Buy or Sell: Hyped Teams by Division
itunes:title: 109:  Best 5 Defensive Players & Buy or Sell: Hyped Teams by Division
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks each list their top 5 defensive players headed into the 2016 season. The guys also go around the league and either buy into the hype or sell the pretenders in each division.  Plus, DJ and producer Sully congratulate Bucky on his winning team at The Opening.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
